{"tid":505953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【樂視自盡】蕭若元又燈中！2年前預測樂視稱霸電視界","createTime":"2017-12-21T16:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-21T17:10:59.000Z","uid":38795,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6394aa5f15ca6ee91d8af2c325f44b8738805552","tid":505953,"uid":38795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T16:35:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171221/57610571\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171221%2F57610571&d=nL7egrjVVTLOIcUIcKoS8CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=165cd20e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171221%2F57610571&h=f0c6b62a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171221/57610571</a><br />\n樂視香港自行清盤，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">連登網民又發現「燈神」蕭若元</span></strong>，原來早在2015年，已大讚樂視能於香港電視爭霸戰中突圍，紛紛高呼「蕭生好嘢」！他於片中稱「樂視具備了擊敗TVB的條件」，數十億投得英超轉播權、平價賣電視，用戶廣泛，廣告收益龐大，而且目標為重奪整個華人社會的市場，雄霸華人社會；他又認為在樂視影響下，有線和NowTV客源應下跌3、4成，TVB平均收視亦在樂視啟播後，下跌到19點左右，1年後跌至15點，5年內轉盈為虧。<br />\n<br />\n蕭若元「燈力」向來備受網民吹捧，他就港大退聯、英國脫歐、特朗普勝選等的預測均悉數落空，今次被「考古」出樂視稱霸評論，就有網民問蕭有沒有講過股票，看來一眾財經燈神要嚴陣以待了。<br />\n<br />\n燒山好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1627fd7a07df34352d725f4ecaac0ba3dac1b042","tid":505953,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T17:10:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}